rows.label: qst200707_msg0002
rows.name: Y-you guys?! When did you get here-mau?

rows.label: qst200707_msg0003
rows.name:
This area is indeed full of monsters, so
collecting the lightly glowing feather
without a Blade is quite a task, mo.

rows.label: qst200707_msg0004
rows.name:
Th-that's not true-mau! Maumau
already has a plan-mau!

rows.label: qst200707_msg0005
rows.name:
You all can go play
with the monsters-mau!

rows.label: qst200707_msg0007
rows.name:
Maybe with Idaten's speed,
he could grab it without
the monsters noticing?

rows.label: qst200707_msg0009
rows.name: Shall we have Idaten get it?

rows.label: qst200707_msg0012
rows.name: I'll go get it in a flash-ppo!!

rows.label: qst200707_msg0013
rows.name:
That's a bit difficult-ppo! At my
current speed, I'll be spotted-ppo!

rows.label: qst200707_msg0014
rows.name:
No, it's dangerous to send Idaten
alone. We should all go together.

rows.label: qst200707_msg0015
rows.name:
Then we have no choice but
to push through while
driving off the monsters.
